---
// src/pages/about.astro
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About">
    <section class="about-section">
        <h2>About Me</h2>
        <p class="intro">Hello, I'm Hugo D Souza, a passionate developer and tech enthusiast.</p>
        <p>This blog is a place where I share my thoughts and experiences with web development, especially using modern tools like Astro.</p>

        <div class="details">
            <h3>My Journey</h3>
            <p>
                I started my journey in web development several years ago, and since then, I've worked on various projects ranging from small personal websites
                to large-scale enterprise applications. My passion lies in creating efficient, scalable, and user-friendly web experiences.
            </p>

            <h3>Skills</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Frontend Development: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React, Astro</li>
                <li>Backend Development: Node.js, Express, MongoDB</li>
                <li>DevOps: Docker, CI/CD, AWS</li>
                <li>Version Control: Git, GitHub</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Projects</h3>
            <p>Here are some of the projects I've worked on:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Project Alpha:</strong> A responsive e-commerce website built with React and Node.js.</li>
                <li><strong>Project Beta:</strong> A blog platform using Astro for static site generation.</li>
                <li><strong>Project Gamma:</strong> A real-time chat application using WebSockets and MongoDB.</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Contact Me</h3>
            <p>If you'd like to get in touch, feel free to reach out via email at <a href="mailto:hugo.dsouza@yahoo.com">hugo.dsouza@yahoo.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>

<style>
    .about-section {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background: #f9f9f9;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    h2 {
        text-align: center;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .intro {
        font-size: 1.2em;
        text-align: center;
        color: #555;
    }

    .details {
        margin-top: 20px;
    }

    h3 {
        color: #444;
        margin-top: 20px;
    }

    ul {
        list-style-type: disc;
        margin-left: 20px;
    }

    li {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: #666;
    }

    a {
        color: #0077cc;
        text-decoration: none;
    }

    a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
    }
</style>
